<body class="bg-light">
  <div class="container">
    <img class="ax-center my-10 w-24" src="/logo.png" />
    <div class="card p-6 p-lg-10 space-y-4">
      <h1 class="h3 fw-700">
        Please clear the oustanding deposit
      </h1>
      <p>
        Hello, <%= @r.booking.guest_name || ' dear guest'%>. You have been requested to pay a deposit for your booking with Casa Cosy. Please use the link below. Booking details for reference:
      </p>
      <table class="table table-striped table-bordered">
        <tr>
          <th>Booking Reference</th>
          <td><%= @r.booking.reference_id %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <th>Dates</th>
          <td><%= @r.booking.arrival %> - <%= @r.booking.departure %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <th>Platform</th>
          <td><%= @r.booking.channel.name %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <th>Flat Name</th>
          <td><%= @r.booking.apartment.name %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <th>Total</th>
          <td>£<%= number_with_precision(@r.booking.price, precision: 2) %></td>
        </tr>
      </table>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col">Deposit total:</div>
        <div class="col text-end"><h3 style='text-align:right; '>£150.00</h3></div>
      </div>
      <p>This is a pre-authorised payment, which means we do not collect the funds ourselves; we instead request your bank to hold the deposit amount in your bank until you check-out.</p>
      <p>This is a security mechsnism for us to ensure the terms for the flat are abided by.</p>

      <a class="btn btn-primary p-3 fw-700" href="/requests/<%= @r.id %>?r=<%= @r.booking.reservation_id %>">Pay Deposit</a>
    </div>
    <div class="text-muted text-center my-6">
      Sent with <3 from Casa Cosy. <br>
      53 Bradford Street<br>
      Walsall, WS1 3QD <br>
      support@casacosy.co.uk
    </div>
  </div>
</body>